            "notes": "This deck is built around the powerful ability of Winota, Joiner of Forces to put non-human creatures into play whenever a human attacks. The main strategy is to flood the board with small aggressive creatures that can trigger Winota's ability multiple times each turn, overwhelming the opponent with a constant stream of threats. By utilizing cards that provide additional combat tricks, protection, and disruption, the deck aims to maintain pressure and create advantageous board states. The inclusion of powerful creature cards and removal spells further enhances the deck's ability to close out games quickly. With a focus on aggressive plays and synergy between creatures, this deck aims to overwhelm opponents in fast-paced one-on-one matches."
